    • moveOne

      public boolean moveOne​(Direction direction)
      Parameters:
      direction - the moving direction
      Returns:
      true, if the robot has been moved successfully, false, if it couldn't be moved moves robot one field, if there's no wall/other obstacle or another robot If there's another robot blocking this field, that robot is moved forward, too.

    • moveOne

      Parameters:
      direction - the moving direction
      ignoreReboot - lets robot move even if it already rebooted (false by default)
      Returns:
      true, if the robot has been moved successfully, false, if it couldn't be moved moves robot one field, if there's no wall/other obstacle or another robot If there's another robot blocking this field, that robot is moved forward, too.
